3. System Requirements and Installation
*****************************************

The system requirements and installation procedure are detailed online
at:

  http://wiki.orbeon.com/forms/doc/developer-guide/admin-installing

In addition, the Orbeon Forms tutorial also tackles installation. Online version:

  http://www.orbeon.com/orbeon/doc/intro-tutorial


